<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Return to Throw Program</title>
<link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Throw Program">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0f2744">
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Barlow:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');
:root {
  --bg: #f2f0eb;
  --card: #ffffff;
  --border: #d8d2c8;
  --navy: #0f2744;
  --text: #1e1e1e;
  --muted: #6e6860;
  --green: #1e6b45;
  --green-light: #e6f4ee;
  --accent: #b83220;
  --accent-light: #fce8e5;
  --yellow: #a06000;
  --yellow-light: #fef4d8;
  --blue: #1155aa;
  --blue-light: #e4ecf9;

  --l1: #0f4c75;
  --l2: #1b6ca8;
  --l3: #1a6b3c;
  --l4: #2d6a4f;
  --l5: #6b3d9a;
  --l6: #8b1a11;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); min-height: 100vh; padding: 0 0 60px; }
.wrap { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 16px; }

/* TOAST */
.toast { position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; background: var(--green); color: white; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .06em; padding: 7px 14px; border-radius: 20px; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); transition: opacity .25s, transform .25s; pointer-events: none; z-index: 999; }
.toast.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

/* HEADER */
.header { background: var(--navy); color: white; border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0; padding: 28px 32px 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 24px; }
.header::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50px; right: -50px; width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(27,108,168,.18); }
.header::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -30px; left: 60px; width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(15,76,117,.15); }
.header-tag { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #5badea; background: rgba(91,173,234,.12); display: inline-block; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.header h1 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -.02em; line-height: 1.2; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.header-meta { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.meta-item { background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.11); border-radius: 8px; padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 13px; }
.meta-item span { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: #8fa8c8; display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; }

/* BACK LINK */
.back-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 0 14px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); margin-top: 16px; display: block; }
.back-link:hover { color: white; }

/* LEVEL TABS */
.tabs-outer { background: var(--card); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-top: none; padding: 16px 20px; }
.tabs-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 10px; }
.tabs-bar { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.tab-btn { position: relative; overflow: hidden; flex: 1; min-width: 100px; background: var(--bg); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s; }
.tab-btn.lv-active { box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="1"].lv-active { border-color: var(--l1); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="2"].lv-active { border-color: var(--l2); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="3"].lv-active { border-color: var(--l3); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="4"].lv-active { border-color: var(--l4); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="5"].lv-active { border-color: var(--l5); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="6"].lv-active { border-color: var(--l6); }
.tab-fill { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; height: 100%; border-radius: 6px; transition: width .5s ease; opacity: .1; pointer-events: none; }
.tab-btn[data-lv="1"] .tab-fill { background: var(--l1); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="2"] .tab-fill { background: var(--l2); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="3"] .tab-fill { background: var(--l3); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="4"] .tab-fill { background: var(--l4); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="5"] .tab-fill { background: var(--l5); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="6"] .tab-fill { background: var(--l6); }
.tab-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.tab-lv-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2px; }
.tab-btn[data-lv="1"].lv-active .tab-lv-label { color: var(--l1); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="2"].lv-active .tab-lv-label { color: var(--l2); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="3"].lv-active .tab-lv-label { color: var(--l3); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="4"].lv-active .tab-lv-label { color: var(--l4); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="5"].lv-active .tab-lv-label { color: var(--l5); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="6"].lv-active .tab-lv-label { color: var(--l6); }
.tab-dist { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); }
.tab-dates { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; line-height: 1.4; }
.tab-prog { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-top: 6px; }
.tab-track { flex: 1; height: 4px; background: #e2ddd6; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; }
.tab-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 20px; transition: width .5s; }
.tab-btn[data-lv="1"] .tab-bar-fill { background: var(--l1); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="2"] .tab-bar-fill { background: var(--l2); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="3"] .tab-bar-fill { background: var(--l3); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="4"] .tab-bar-fill { background: var(--l4); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="5"] .tab-bar-fill { background: var(--l5); }
.tab-btn[data-lv="6"] .tab-bar-fill { background: var(--l6); }
.tab-count { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); white-space: nowrap; }

/* PANELS */
.level-panel { display: none; padding-top: 18px; }
.level-panel.active { display: block; }

/* LEVEL FOCUS */
.level-focus { border-radius: 8px; padding: 13px 18px; margin-bottom: 14px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.65; }
.lf1 { background: #e6f0fa; border: 1.5px solid #90bce8; color: #0a3a5c; }
.lf2 { background: #e2eef8; border: 1.5px solid #6aaee0; color: #0e4a7a; }
.lf3 { background: var(--green-light); border: 1.5px solid #8ecfaa; color: #134d2c; }
.lf4 { background: #e6f2ec; border: 1.5px solid #7dc4a0; color: #1a4d35; }
.lf5 { background: #f0eaf8; border: 1.5px solid #c09de0; color: #4a2270; }
.lf6 { background: var(--accent-light); border: 1.5px solid #e8a09a; color: #6e1208; }

/* CRITERIA BLOCKS */
.crit { border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; }
.crit-pre { background: #fffbec; border: 1.5px solid #f5d87a; }
.crit-in  { background: #fef0f0; border: 1.5px solid #f5a8a8; }
.crit-mech { background: var(--blue-light); border: 1.5px solid #a0bce8; }
.crit-post { background: #eef0fa; border: 1.5px solid #a8b8e8; }
.crit-title { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-bottom: 7px; }
.crit-pre .crit-title { color: #9a7000; }
.crit-in .crit-title  { color: #a02020; }
.crit-mech .crit-title { color: #1155aa; }
.crit-post .crit-title { color: #2233aa; }
.crit ul { padding-left: 16px; margin: 0; }
.crit li { margin-bottom: 3px; }
.crit strong { font-weight: 700; }

/* SESSION CARDS */
.session-card { background: var(--card); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; overflow: hidden; transition: box-shadow .2s; }
.session-card.completed { border-color: #8ecfaa; }
.session-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 3px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.07); }
.session-head { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 13px 18px; gap: 12px; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--border); background: #fafaf8; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.session-card.completed .session-head { background: var(--green-light); border-bottom-color: #8ecfaa; }
.session-num { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--navy); min-width: 30px; }
.session-info { flex: 1; min-width: 140px; }
.session-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
.session-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
.session-tags { display: flex; gap: 5px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.stag { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 20px; }
.stag-dist { background: var(--blue-light); color: var(--blue); }
.stag-vol  { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); }
.stag-game { background: var(--yellow-light); color: var(--yellow); }
.session-status { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); background: var(--bg); padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); white-space: nowrap; }
.session-card.completed .session-status { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); border-color: #8ecfaa; }
.session-body { padding: 16px 18px 18px; display: none; }
.session-body.open { display: block; }

/* SETS */
.sets-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 7px; }
.sets-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.set-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; background: var(--bg); border-radius: 7px; padding: 9px 12px; border: 1.5px solid transparent; transition: border-color .15s, background .15s; }
.set-row.set-done { background: var(--green-light); border-color: #8ecfaa; }
.set-check { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 6px; border: 2px solid var(--border); background: white; cursor: pointer; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; transition: all .15s; }
.set-row.set-done .set-check { background: var(--green); border-color: var(--green); color: white; }
.set-desc { flex: 1; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); }
.set-detail { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5; }
.set-badge { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 7px; white-space: nowrap; }
.rest-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 3px 12px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }
.rest-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

/* NOTES */
.notes-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
@media(max-width:560px) { .notes-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.notes-box label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
.notes-box textarea { width: 100%; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 7px; background: var(--bg); padding: 9px 11px; font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); resize: vertical; min-height: 68px; line-height: 1.5; transition: border-color .15s; }
.notes-box textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--navy); background: white; }
.notes-box textarea::placeholder { color: #b0a898; }

/* PT REVIEW */
.pt-review { background: #f0f4ff; border: 1.5px solid #c0d0f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; margin-top: 12px; }
.pt-review-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #3050c0; margin-bottom: 7px; }
.pt-review textarea { width: 100%; border: 1.5px solid #c0d0f0; border-radius: 7px; background: white; padding: 9px 11px; font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); resize: vertical; min-height: 76px; line-height: 1.5; }

/* ADVANCE BOX */
.adv-box { background: var(--navy); color: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 18px 22px; margin-top: 6px; }
.adv-box .adv-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7090b8; margin-bottom: 7px; }
.adv-box h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 7px; }
.adv-box p { font-size: 13px; color: #c0d0e4; line-height: 1.8; }
.adv-box .hl { color: #f8c96b; font-weight: 700; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="toast" id="toast">✓ Saved</div>

<div class="wrap">

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="header-tag">⚾ Return to Sport — Post-SLAP Repair</div>
  <h1>Return to Throw Program</h1>
  <div class="header-meta">
    <div class="meta-item"><span>Levels</span>6 distance levels</div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span>Sessions</span>12 total</div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span>Ceiling</span>120 feet</div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span>Started</span>Mar 13, 2026</div>
  </div>
  <a class="back-link" href="index.html">← Back to Hitting Program</a>
</div>

<!-- TABS -->
<div class="tabs-outer">
  <div class="tabs-label">Distance Level</div>
  <div class="tabs-bar">

    <button class="tab-btn lv-active" data-lv="1" onclick="switchLevel(1)">
      <div class="tab-fill" id="tf-1" style="width:0%"></div>
      <div class="tab-inner">
        <div class="tab-lv-label">Level 1</div>
        <div class="tab-dist">45'</div>
        <div class="tab-dates">Mon 3/16<br>Wed 3/18</div>
        <div class="tab-prog">
          <div class="tab-track"><div class="tab-bar-fill" id="tb-1" style="width:0%"></div></div>
          <div class="tab-count" id="tc-1">0/2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </button>

    <button class="tab-btn" data-lv="2" onclick="switchLevel(2)">
      <div class="tab-fill" id="tf-2" style="width:0%"></div>
      <div class="tab-inner">
        <div class="tab-lv-label">Level 2</div>
        <div class="tab-dist">60'</div>
        <div class="tab-dates">Sat 3/21<br>Mon 3/23</div>
        <div class="tab-prog">
          <div class="tab-track"><div class="tab-bar-fill" id="tb-2" style="width:0%"></div></div>
          <div class="tab-count" id="tc-2">0/2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </button>

    <button class="tab-btn" data-lv="3" onclick="switchLevel(3)">
      <div class="tab-fill" id="tf-3" style="width:0%"></div>
      <div class="tab-inner">
        <div class="tab-lv-label">Level 3</div>
        <div class="tab-dist">75'</div>
        <div class="tab-dates">Thu 3/26<br>Sat 3/28</div>
        <div class="tab-prog">
          <div class="tab-track"><div class="tab-bar-fill" id="tb-3" style="width:0%"></div></div>
          <div class="tab-count" id="tc-3">0/2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </button>

    <button class="tab-btn" data-lv="4" onclick="switchLevel(4)">
      <div class="tab-fill" id="tf-4" style="width:0%"></div>
      <div class="tab-inner">
        <div class="tab-lv-label">Level 4</div>
        <div class="tab-dist">90'</div>
        <div class="tab-dates">Mon 3/30<br>Wed 4/1</div>
        <div class="tab-prog">
          <div class="tab-track"><div class="tab-bar-fill" id="tb-4" style="width:0%"></div></div>
          <div class="tab-count" id="tc-4">0/2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </button>

    <button class="tab-btn" data-lv="5" onclick="switchLevel(5)">
      <div class="tab-fill" id="tf-5" style="width:0%"></div>
      <div class="tab-inner">
        <div class="tab-lv-label">Level 5</div>
        <div class="tab-dist">105'</div>
        <div class="tab-dates">Sat 4/4<br>Mon 4/6</div>
        <div class="tab-prog">
          <div class="tab-track"><div class="tab-bar-fill" id="tb-5" style="width:0%"></div></div>
          <div class="tab-count" id="tc-5">0/2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </button>

    <button class="tab-btn" data-lv="6" onclick="switchLevel(6)">
      <div class="tab-fill" id="tf-6" style="width:0%"></div>
      <div class="tab-inner">
        <div class="tab-lv-label">Level 6</div>
        <div class="tab-dist">120'</div>
        <div class="tab-dates">Thu 4/9<br>Sat 4/11</div>
        <div class="tab-prog">
          <div class="tab-track"><div class="tab-bar-fill" id="tb-6" style="width:0%"></div></div>
          <div class="tab-count" id="tc-6">0/2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </button>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════ SHARED CRITERIA (injected per panel via JS) ═══════ -->
<template id="tpl-criteria">
  <div class="crit crit-pre">
    <span class="crit-title">⚠️ Pre-Session Check</span>
    <ul>
      <li>Warm up first: arm circles, band ER, shoulder CARs — 5 min</li>
      <li>If lingering soreness from prior session <strong>does not improve</strong> during warm-up tosses → <strong>hold today, try tomorrow</strong></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="crit crit-in">
    <span class="crit-title">🛑 In-Session Modification Criteria</span>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Soreness builds to &gt;4/10:</strong> Stop — 5 min full rest — reassess. If it doesn't settle → session over for the day</li>
      <li><strong>Sharp pain at any point:</strong> Stop immediately. Do not restart. Contact PT before next session</li>
      <li><strong>Mechanics breakdown (stop or reduce intensity if):</strong> arm path rises above shoulder on release, short-arming under fatigue, trunk dragging arm instead of hip/trunk leading, throwing shoulder hikes or fails to decelerate smoothly</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="crit crit-mech">
    <span class="crit-title">🎯 Optimal Mechanics Targets</span>
    <ul>
      <li>Hip and trunk rotation initiates — arm follows. If the arm is leading, reset</li>
      <li>Arm path at or below shoulder height through release — no high-and-late pattern</li>
      <li>Full arm arc on every throw — no short-arming as distance or fatigue increases</li>
      <li>Smooth follow-through with controlled deceleration — no abrupt stop or shoulder hike</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</template>

<template id="tpl-post">
  <div class="crit crit-post">
    <span class="crit-title">🌙 Post-Session Hold Criteria</span>
    <ul>
      <li>Next-day soreness lasting <strong>&gt;24 hours</strong> → repeat this level before progressing</li>
      <li>Soreness surpassing <strong>6/10</strong> at any point post-session → hold</li>
      <li>Soreness that interferes with strength/rehab work → hold</li>
      <li>Any sharp or new symptom pattern → contact PT before next session</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</template>

<!-- ═══════════════ LEVEL 1 — 45' ═══════════════ -->
<div class="level-panel active" id="panel-1">
  <div class="level-focus lf1">
    <strong>Level 1 — 45 feet &nbsp;·&nbsp; Mon 3/16 &amp; Wed 3/18</strong><br>
    First full-distance session. Bridge work (20' and 30') is complete. Keep effort easy and controlled — 60–70%. The goal is mechanics quality and tissue tolerance, not arm strength. <em>Bridge note: Fri 3/14 — 30' × 2×20 throws complete.</em>
  </div>

  <!-- S1 -->
  <div class="session-card" id="card-L1S1">
    <div class="session-head" onclick="toggleSession('L1S1')">
      <div class="session-num">S1</div>
      <div class="session-info">
        <div class="session-title">45' — 1 × 25 throws</div>
        <div class="session-sub">Mon 3/16 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Rest + strength day follows</div>
      </div>
      <div class="session-tags">
        <span class="stag stag-dist">45 feet</span>
        <span class="stag stag-vol">1 × 25</span>
      </div>
      <div class="session-status" id="status-L1S1">Not started</div>
    </div>
    <div class="session-body open" id="body-L1S1">
      <div class="sets-label">Sets — tap to mark complete</div>
      <div class="sets-grid" id="sets-L1S1">
        <div class="set-row" id="s-L1S1-1">
          <div class="set-check" onclick="toggleSet('s-L1S1-1','L1S1')"></div>
          <div class="set-desc">Set 1 — 25 Throws
            <div class="set-detail">45 feet. 60–70% effort. Smooth, fluid release. Full arm arc. Hip leads the throw every rep.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="set-badge">45' · 25</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="post-L1S1"></div>
      <div class="notes-grid">
        <div class="notes-box"><label>🩺 During-Session</label><textarea id="ta-L1S1-d" placeholder="Shoulder feel at 45'. Posterior soreness? Any sharp sensation? Rate 0–10."></textarea></div>
        <div class="notes-box"><label>🌙 Next-Day</label><textarea id="ta-L1S1-n" placeholder="Next-day soreness. Location, level. Better or worse than bridge sessions?"></textarea></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- S2 -->
  <div class="session-card" id="card-L1S2">
    <div class="session-head" onclick="toggleSession('L1S2')">
